  "notes": "All implementable P0/P1/P2 issues resolved. Three P1 architectural issues remain open and flagged for human decision: wolfssl-rs-3i8 (client shape), wolfssl-rs-fcd (RustCrypto traits), wolfssl-rs-to7 (Drop eviction).",
